20
00:03:06.102 --> 00:03:07.937
Hey, how you doing, little housewife?

21
00:03:08.021 --> 00:03:09.772
You all packed? We're out of here tonight.

22
00:03:09.856 --> 00:03:12.400
Well, wait now.
I still have to ask Darryl if I can go.

23
00:03:12.483 --> 00:03:14.986
You mean you haven't asked him yet?

24
00:03:15.069 --> 00:03:17.488
