25
00:03:17.572 --> 00:03:20.116
Thelma, is he your husband or your father?

26
00:03:20.199 --> 00:03:22.452
It is just two days, for God's sake.

27
00:03:22.535 --> 00:03:25.621
Don't be a child.
Tell him you're going with me.

28
00:03:25.705 --> 00:03:27.749
Tell him I'm having a nervous breakdown.

29
00:03:27.832 --> 00:03:31.169
