Have a good day at work today.

46
00:04:18.174 --> 00:04:19.384
Uh-huh.

47
00:04:20.885 --> 00:04:22.720
- Jesus.
- Here.

48
00:04:22.804 --> 00:04:24.097
Thank you, no.

49
