Christ, I gotta get to work!

62
00:05:12.728 --> 00:05:15.231
Don't need this bullshit in the morning!

63
00:05:15.314 --> 00:05:17.483
Just leave 'em. I'll get 'em. Thank you.

64
00:05:18.276 --> 00:05:19.861
For Christ's sakes.

65
00:05:21.112 --> 00:05:23.114
<i>(Engine starts)</i>

66
00:05:23.197 --> 00:05:27.785
And I want you out of here by 5:00.
No, 3:00. Get out of here by 3:00 today.

67
00:05:30.872 --> 00:05:32.081
<i>(Tires screech)</i>

68
00:05:32.165 --> 00:05:34.292
<i>(Phone rings)</i>

69
00:05:34.375 --> 00:05:35.418
Good morning.

70
00:05:35.501 --> 00:05:39.005
