Hey, what did he say?

74
00:05:45.261 --> 00:05:46.971
What time are you picking me up?

75
00:05:47.054 --> 00:05:50.183
<i>Allright!
Uh, I'll be there around 2:00 or 3:00.</i>

76
00:05:50.266 --> 00:05:51.267
Okay.

77
00:05:51.350 --> 00:05:53.144
Hey, say, what kind of stuff do I bring?

78
00:05:53.227 --> 00:05:55.146
Oh, I don't know. Warm stuff, I guess.

79
00:05:55.229 --> 00:05:58.900
It's the mountains. It gets cold at night.
I'm just gonna bring everything.

80
00:05:58.983 --> 00:06:01.486
Okay. I will too, then.

81
00:06:02.028 --> 00:06:05.364
<i>- And steal Darryl's fishing stuff.</i>
- Louise, I don't know how to fish.

82
00:06:05.448 --> 00:06:08.326
Neither do I, Thelma, but Darryl does it.
How hard can it be?

83
00:06:08.409 --> 00:06:09.494
<i>(Laughs)</i>

84
00:06:09.577 --> 00:06:11.579
- All right, I'll see you in a bit.
- Okay.

85
00:06:11.662 --> 00:06:12.914
Okay, bye.

86
00:06:12.997 --> 00:06:16.501
- <i>(Hammer banging in distance)</i>
- <i>(Chattering on TV continues)</i>

87
00:06:18.085 --> 00:06:19.295
