91
00:06:38.439 --> 00:06:41.526
<i>♪ And stand before the mirror ♪</i>

92
00:06:43.152 --> 00:06:45.279
<i>♪ And you comb your hair ♪</i>

93
00:06:45.363 --> 00:06:47.823
<i>♪ And grab your coat and hat ♪</i>

94
00:06:49.825 --> 00:06:55.331
<i>♪ And you walk the wet streets
