96
00:07:02.547 --> 00:07:06.842
<i>♪ And everything looks so complete ♪</i>

97
00:07:06.926 --> 00:07:09.136
<i>♪ When you're walkin' out on the street... ♪</i>

98
00:07:09.220 --> 00:07:13.683
<i>(Voice mail)</i> <i>Hi, this is Jimmy.
